727953f-a.title: Queens: Sanford Avenue - Kissena Boulevard
727953f-a.text:
Sanford Avenue, north side, about 100 feet vest of Kissena Soulevard, showing the S. Vernon mansion. In 1873 M. Hoffman, and in 1891 S.V. Mann vere the owners . Jaggar Avenue a street west of the house, in 1837, ras a private lane leading fror Main Street to the Jaggar house. A Bundav Bchool or Synagoge occupied the house in 1934. It is exempt for tax purposes and is registered
in the name of E. Mann in 1934.
1922
